investigation.title: Plant Gravity Perception (PGP) Flight Study
investigation.description: This study investigated plant responses to a range of gravity treatments. Altered gravity was achieved by growing seedlings on the ISS within the centrifuge of the European Modular Cultivation System (EMCS) and applying a specific rotation rate for a fixed time in the experiment.

project.title: Characterizing Plant Gravity Perception Systems
project.funding: 2014 Space Biology Flight (ILSRA) NNH14ZTT002N , Grant/Contract No.: NNX15AG55G
